lead_paragraph: Defender Birkir Mar Saeverson fired a stunning goal as Iceland romped to a 4-0 win over Liechtenstein in Reykjavik on Monday in their final tune-up ahead of Euro 2016.

headline.print_headline: Iceland Thrash Liechtenstein 4-0 in Final Euro Warm-Up
